text: Jessica Winter is an American bioengineer currently at Ohio State University and an Elected Fellow of the American Association for the Advancement of Science. Her sister Jodie Lutkenhaus is a Professor of Chemical Engineering at Texas A&M; University. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Fellows of the American Association for the Advancement of Science Category:21st-century American engineers Category:Ohio State University faculty
